last_episode_to_air.name: The Hollow Heart
last_episode_to_air.overview: This is the incredible story of a tree that has been around for eight hundred years - that can withstand the harshest conditions - and that is more loved by insects, birds and animals than any other - an enormous Baobab rooted on the Savannah of Malilangwe Game Reserve in southern Zimbabwe.

name: Rooted Life Through The Eyes Of Trees
original_name: Rooted Life Through The Eyes Of Trees
overview: Rooted is the story of five iconic trees in found in a Southern Africa. Each tree is located in a completely unique habitat, and hosts, feeds and shelters an array of insects, birds and animals in the bows of its branches.
